    "text": [
        "Nowadays, shopping has gone to a next level and credit for this goes to many online websites and apps which enables this feature. However there are various benefits and risks associated with online shopping.",
        "Today\u2019s generations are more aware about the various types of product available in the market as product from A to Z is available online. Online shopping helps in increasing the purchasing power of the customer as online platform gives huge discounts on the products. Along with money it also saves the time of the people as they can do shopping by sitting at their home. Nowadays many online shopping platform like Myntra, flip kart  etc. Gives easy refund policy, such as by adding 1 rupees you can get the option of trial of cloths like if a buyer does not like a particular shirt then he can refund that shirt on the spot to them.",
        "With increase in online shopping there also increases in the risk associated with it. In many online shopping platform consumer is getting cheated in various ways, such as the amount gets credited from your account but the consumer does not get their product. They also do not give the consumer the product guarantee. There was one case that happened to one of the customers in which he ordered an iPhone from an online website, but instead of the iPhone he received stones in the box. So there are many such types of incidents like these in which customer is getting cheated by this type of online shopping platform.",
        "To sum up, there are many risks and benefit associated with online shopping so the consumer should be aware of all the risk associated with these and should be aware of various fake sites on the other hand they should also take the benefits of shopping goods online."
